     1→/**
     2→ * banner.css — Banner Section Component
     3→ * ========================================
     4→ * Full-width gradient banner with fluid heading typography.
     5→ * Mobile-first: base styles for smallest screen; min-width queries upward.
     6→ *
     7→ * Usage: <div class="banner"><h2 class="banner-title">…</h2></div>
     8→ */
     9→
    10→/* ===== BANNER CONTAINER ===== */
    11→/* Mobile base */
